name: Mini jam 79: Frogs (Only one Level) - Feed the Frog!
name_original: Mini jam 79: Frogs (Only one Level) - Feed the Frog!
description:
Made in 72 hours for the Mini jam game jam

Catch the flies with your tongue whilst avoiding eating the poison flies,and get the highest score!

Controls

WASD / ARROW KEYS - Move

Left Click - Melee

Right Click - Tongue

Space - Jump

Esc - Pause
